value: Resident, wetlands mixed with grassland, savanna: eastern Africa S Uganda, SW Kenya - E South Africa extending west in S Angola, N Namibia.

mixture of wetlands, grasslands & open savanna.in E Africa mostly found now in human-modified habitats, including pastures, croplands, fallow fields.irrigated areas & ranches.In S Africa, marshes and vleis in grassland & savanna;also agricultural land
